OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F416A1779372669
OL,3,CSouthampton lose appeal against play-
OL,4,Coff expulsion over spying on opponents
OL,6,FSouthampton have lost their appeal
OL,7,Fagainst being expelled from the
OL,8,FChampionship play-offs over spying on
OL,9,Fopponents.
OL,11,FIt means that Middlesbrough will face
OL,12,FHull in Saturday's play-off final,
OL,13,Fwith the game kicking off at 3.30pm.
OL,15,FSaints had previously admitted to
OL,16,Fspying on three occasions during the
OL,17,Fseason, on Oxford United in December
OL,18,F2025, on Ipswich Town in April 2026
OL,19,Fand on Middlesbrough before their play-
OL,20,Foff semi-final earlier this month.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/9
