PN,41602
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F416A1779372669
OL,3,CSouthampton lose appeal against play-
OL,4,Coff expulsion over spying on opponents
OL,6,FA disciplinary commission threw
OL,7,FSouthampton out of the play-offs on
OL,8,FTuesday (19 May), and reinstated their
OL,9,Fsemi-final opponents Middlesbrough,
OL,10,Fsending them through to the final
OL,11,Fagainst Hull at Wembley on Saturday
OL,12,F(23 May).
OL,14,FDespite arguing that the decision was
OL,15,F'manifestly disproportionate', the
OL,16,Foriginal decision has been upheld.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/9
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
