OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,417,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41603
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F416A1779372669
OL,3,CSouthampton lose appeal against play-
OL,4,Coff expulsion over spying on opponents
OL,6,FIn a statement a spokesperson said:
OL,7,F"This is an extremely disappointing
OL,8,Foutcome for everybody connected with
OL,9,FSouthampton Football Club. We know how
OL,10,Fpainful this moment will be for our
OL,11,Fsupporters, players, staff, commercial
OL,12,Fpartners and the wider community who
OL,13,Fhave given so much backing to the team
OL,14,Fthroughout the season and we apologise
OL,15,Fonce again to everyone impacted by
OL,16,Fthis.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/9
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,417,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41604
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F416A1779372669
OL,3,CSouthampton lose appeal against play-
OL,4,Coff expulsion over spying on opponents
OL,6,F"While we fully acknowledge the
OL,7,Fseriousness of this matter and the
OL,8,Fscrutiny that has followed, the club
OL,9,Fhas consistently believed the original
OL,10,Fsporting sanction was
OL,11,Fdisproportionate, a view that has been
OL,12,Fwidely shared by many in the football
OL,13,Fcommunity over the last 24 hours.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/9
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,417,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41605
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F416A1779372669
OL,3,CSouthampton lose appeal against play-
OL,4,Coff expulsion over spying on opponents
OL,6,F"We would like to place on record our
OL,7,Fsincere thanks to our supporters for
OL,8,Fthe support, patience and loyalty they
OL,9,Fhave shown throughout an incredibly
OL,10,Fdifficult period. We will share
OL,11,Finformation as soon as possible in
OL,12,Frelation to ticket refunds for those
OL,13,Fwho bought tickets to Wembley.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G5/9
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,417,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41606
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F416A1779372669
OL,3,CSouthampton lose appeal against play-
OL,4,Coff expulsion over spying on opponents
OL,6,F"Southampton Football Club has a proud
OL,7,Fhistory and strong foundations, but it
OL,8,Fis clear that trust now needs to be
OL,9,Frebuilt. That work begins immediately.
OL,10,FThe club will reflect carefully on the
OL,11,Fevents that have led to this point,
OL,12,Flearn from them and take the necessary
OL,13,Fsteps to move forward responsibly.
OL,15,F"While tonight is a painful moment,
OL,16,Fthis football club will respond with
OL,17,Fhumility, accountability and
OL,18,Fdetermination to put things right."
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G6/9
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
