PN,41607
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F416A1779372669
OL,3,CSouthampton lose appeal against play-
OL,4,Coff expulsion over spying on opponents
OL,6,FSouthampton appealed the decision,
OL,7,Fsaying on Wednesday before the appeal
OL,8,Foutcome that the punishment was
OL,9,F"manifestly disproportionate to every
OL,10,Fprevious sanction in the history of
OL,11,Fthe English game."
OL,13,FThey also apologised to the other
OL,14,Fclubs involved, and to their own fans,
OL,15,Fwho they said "deserved better" for
OL,16,Ftheir "extraordinary loyalty and
OL,17,Fsupport."
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G7/9
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
