FL,417,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41608
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F416A1779372669
OL,3,CSouthampton lose appeal against play-
OL,4,Coff expulsion over spying on opponents
OL,6,FHowever, Middlesbrough described the
OL,7,Foriginal decision as sending out "a
OL,8,Fclear message for the future of our
OL,9,Fgame regarding sporting integrity and
OL,10,Fconduct."
OL,12,FThe 'spygate' scandal all started when
OL,13,FMiddlesbrough reported to the EFL that
OL,14,Fa member of Southampton staff had
OL,15,Fspied on a training session on 7 May,
OL,16,Fin breach of league rules, with the
OL,17,FEFL charging Southampton the following
OL,18,Fday.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G8/9
